defaultQ17 default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultTeresa Pearce:default Dr Carney, if I understood you correctly, I think you just said that you believe that the increase in house prices is down to increasing mortgage availability. Is that what you just said?
defaultDr Carneydefault: No. What I suggested was that the growth in mortgages was a function of increased transactions in the housing market coming off very low
default levels
